OL,7,FThree energy companies have stopped the
OL,8,Fforced installation of prepayment
OL,9,Fmeters after the industry has faced
OL,10,Fmonths of pressure to stop pushing
OL,11,Ffamilies to live in the cold and dark.
OL,13,FShell Energy and Utilita have said they
OL,14,Fhave suspended warrants until the end
OL,15,Fof winter.
OL,17,FTheir decisions follow that of British
OL,18,FGas which announced on Thursday that it
OL,19,Fis suspending all prepayment warrant
OL,20,Factivity "at least until the end of
OL,21,Fwinter".
